For practise purpose , install minikube using below mentioned link.

https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/?arch=%2Fwindows%2Fx86-64%2Fstable%2F.exe+download

Install Kubectl using below mention link.

https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-kubectl-linux/

Note: Kindly make sure that container run time environment like docker is already installed in your virtual machine or EC2 instance otherwise minikube fails to start.
